Heres the chanse to get a free acount, trial and download of one of the Best online MMPORG ever! Grafic is great and the game also has what so many other MMPORG has a lack of, Player feeling! 


For most challange and fun select the Darktide server make new friends or start your own Guild! Or join a Exisiting Guild by swearing allegiance to someone! Great XP reward system if you decide to become a Patron and take vassals (other players) and bring them into your current guild! Or the old school way by leveling up in the woods!

Buy your own house that you easy can recall to where ever you are together with a treasure chest where you can save your most preciouse items. There are lots of classes to choose among and all weapons are very well balanced and good at diffrent kinds of battles! 

Each acount contains 7 empty slots that you can make diffrent kind of characters on! 

